      <textAnnotation id="sid-C61AEB2A-C744-4A6D-8550-F151AA3BC58F" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DD53B78B-B9FD-41BA-94DA-88DF4ED18CB9" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6EDF2137-8839-4D2C-B1A9-5E83A08E196C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If any exceptions identified, decision to be taken whether to again update the OA or not.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-16E173C2-5BCF-4B0A-BCB9-A77E8A65B575" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Legal contract ID from Icertis to be captured by boundary app and feed OA in S4</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-FAE856EB-4ADA-4717-95F7-E440B87AA91A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>•This L3 is applicable for goods and services.
•Process happens inside S4
•This flow is for operational contract in SAP S4 (OA)
•No approval from SAP S4 needed
•Push from CWB is going to create OA in S4
•Legal contract ID needs to be captured by Boundary app and shared to OA in S4 if ICI is not going to be integrated to S4
•Contract ID will be at header level in OA
•Quote ID should be in line level
•CWB is used for equipment and RFX UI for direct materials
•As is – process of matching variances between pricing and OA using CWB is done in equipment
•As- is - SIMS, ODM OSAT  manual
•As is Parts without material number – manual creation of PO through shopping cart not tied to OA or PIR
•This flow is related to items with MMID ( not in early stage of production NPI)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-79E7A54F-4199-4E8A-907E-DEADCB93554E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Nageswaran, Rohan &lt;rohan.nageswaran@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
